Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mail's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be a "yes".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be a "yes".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be a "yes".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She can make it!\NShe can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Going out on a limb here,\Nbut I'm guessing that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance said she\Ncan come this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.17,0:00:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finally going to get to\Nspend some quality time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,with my sister-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best news EVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, so sorry for\Nbarging in like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so excited I just\Ncouldn't wait to tell somepony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Equestrian Society for the\NPreservation of Rare Creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,has given me permission to\Nobserve the rarest, tiniest,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,most adorable magical creatures\Nin all of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Breezies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Fluttershy,\Nthat's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's not just fantastic;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it just might be\Nthe best news EVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got the most incredible\Nmail anypony's ever received
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of recorded\Npony postal history!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a flyer about a one-day\Nsale on used patio furniture!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Could this day\Nget any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a wrap in\Ncase it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I packed you a basket\Nof nice fresh apples
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.01,0:02:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in case you get hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hope you have\Nfun with Cadance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,ALL Aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye! Goodbye, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never\Nforget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, something floaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,La la la la la.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit nervous\Nabout Cadance's visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What could you be\Nnervous about, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Cadance just loves\Nyou to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really want her visit\Nto go without a hitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the last few times\Nwe've seen each other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't exactly\Nbeen "worry free."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The fate of Equestria\Nhas hung in the balance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,during most of\Nyour visits with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Cadance and I haven't\Nreally had a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to just enjoy being\Nfriends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why it is so important\Nthat this visit be about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of us having some\Nreal quality time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessin' you've got a\Nplan that'll keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The timing couldn't\Nbe more perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For one day only, right\Nhere in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The 'Starswirl the\NBearded' Traveling Museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cadance and I can spend\Nthe whole day looking at
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Starswirl the Bearded artifacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like the\Nperfect, drama-free way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to spend the day\Nwith Cadance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not counting the drama\Nsurrounding which of the bells
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,from his cloak they've\Nchosen to put on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoiler alert: It's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, heh heh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Something in my throat\Nlike a big ball of "lame?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it sounds delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Definitely sounds\Nlike you two will have
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,some real quality\Ntime together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just quiet time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm teasing, Twilight.\NWe're sisters-in-law;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have to be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing you, you've\Nmade some plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, have I. Hang on\Njust one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't you\Nworry about a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make sure that\Nnothing, but nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,interferes with your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on! Have a hootenanny\Nwith your kinfolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are the best friends\Na pony could ever have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming, Cadance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Two sisters-in-law bonding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I for one am\Ngonna make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that nothing spoils\Ntheir day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that thing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is...DUCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, That doesn't look\Nanything like a duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not a what{\i0}\N{\i1}but a "who," dear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, that sounds like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,DISCORD!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation\Nare you doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And why the jumpin'\Njunebugs are you blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,More like a shade of\Ncerulean, to be precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever color you are\Nis the color of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rainbow Dash,\NI've changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you remember\NI was reformed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,by lovely little Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sick or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I'm sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The blue skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:05:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,These sneezes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could somebody find\Nme a fainting couch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Charming, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop sneezing\Nand wheezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, I need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're so sick, why have\Nyou come here instead of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,y'know, staying home in bed and\Ngetting over your weird illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this condition\Nhas left me helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I can barely lift a spoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to find the one pony\Nwho truly understands me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and could nurse me\Nback to health.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that dear,\Nsweet Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I need attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I need some care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to chill!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Her trip to see the\NBreezies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah yes, I had forgotten\Nthat was today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know\Nabout her trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me about\Nit in her last letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Fluttershy write\Neach other letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just such a shame\Nthat today of all days
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is when I really need her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. I know\Nwhat to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thinking, head on\Nhome, put your feet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure eventually\Nyou'll have the strength
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to make yourself\Nsoup or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean while she's gone, you\Nponies can take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what\Nfriends are for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking care of\Neach other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the healing begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! That's some way to\Ntreat a suffering friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, Discord,\NI'll give you cuddles
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and read stories and\Ntell you all about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born on a Tuesday....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so sweet to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rarity and Applejack\Nalready volunteered
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to be my own personal\Nnursemaids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I SO hope you don't\Nmind, Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as a matter of\Nfact, I most certainly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who keeps throwing away\Nthese perfectly good balloons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That joker's\Nup to somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And whatever it is, we're\Ngonna keep it as far away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,from Twilight and Princess\NCadance as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised we wouldn't let\Nanything ruin their visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I do so wish that\N"anything" had turned out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I hear you two talking about\NPrincess Cadance's visit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with Princess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy had mentioned\Nthat those two
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,were getting together today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful for them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so rare that those two\Nget to see one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about you, but I\Nsometimes wonder how close
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,they could actually be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All those years apart{\i0}\N{\i1}before being reunited?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're plenty close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they're not, this rare\Nopportunity to focus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,on their friendship will\Ncertainly bring them closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even\Nthink about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They mustn't be disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Disturb them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why I wouldn't dream of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not when I have two such\Ndear friends of my own
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,who have already offered\Nto take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And at such peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This flu of mine is highly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I've gotten\Nyou both sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whomever shall I turn to\Nnow in my time of need?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole day to celebrate\NStarswirl the Bearded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What could be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the candlestick\Nhe used to light the way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,when he was exploring the\Ncaverns of Maretania?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't believe I'm getting\Nto see it in real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord! What are\Nyou doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear, dear Princesses,\NI'm sorry to say I'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Flu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear I've already given it\Nto poor Applejack and Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic health bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How would Twilight\Nnurse me back to health
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,if she was sick, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be letting\Nme stay at your place
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,until I'm all\Nbetter, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, now is not\Nreally the best time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm sure you\Nalready knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But taking in the sick\Nand the desperate:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that what\NFluttershy would do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't "helping" something\Nthat friends do for friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you're really saying that\Nyou're not my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That is not\Nwhat I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how elated I\Nam to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall the three of us\Nhead back to your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get\Nanypony else sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we don't have\Nmuch choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. poo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Need anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just knowing that I have\Na good friend like you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to take care of me has\Nmade me feel better already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine here on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Just before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little, small request.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just get him\Nwhat he wants
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and be back to the\Nexhibit in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it that you needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ A little glass of{\i0}\N{\i1}water, please? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ A fresh-pressed{\i0}\N{\i1}hankie if I sneeze? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Some tea with honey{\i0}\N{\i1}from the bees ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Whenever you can brew it {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ And while I get a little rest\N{\i1}A teeny tiny small request ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Some codfish oil for my chest\N{\i1}Poured from a crystal cruet ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A crystal cruet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ My goodness,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm a nincompoop ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Because I fear I've{\i0}\N{\i1}got the croup ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I need a vat of{\i0}\N{\i1}pumpkin soup ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And scarves made out{\i0}\N{\i1}of zinnias! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Did I say zinnias?{\i0}\N{\i1}I meant silk! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Or something shiny{\i0}\N{\i1}of that ilk, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And then I'll need{\i0}\N{\i1}some nice warm milk ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And pastry from Abyssinia. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And since my stomach's{\i0}\N{\i1}feeling crummy, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Why not give my aching tummy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Something soothing,{\i0}\N{\i1}something yummy ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Piled up with noodles {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ And a slice of homemade rye
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ With stacks of{\i0}\N{\i1}Swiss way up high ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Served with sides{\i0}\N{\i1}of sweet mince pie ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ More basil; I need oodles {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I'll be grateful for{\i0}\N{\i1}your charity ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Until the bitter end {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Because I've heard{\i0}\N{\i1}that tenderness ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Is what you lend{\i0}\N{\i1}an ailing friend ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenderness; isn't\Nthat right, friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So! Who's ready for\Nmy big reprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I'd like my glass{\i0}\N{\i1}of water, please ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Some magic spell{\i0}\N{\i1}to cure disease ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ A firm 'gesundhoof!"{\i0}\N{\i1}when I sneeze ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ A fresh bouquet of roses. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Some lozenges{\i0}\N{\i1}will soon appease ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ My wheezing when I{\i0}\N{\i1}start to sneeze ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ A wig to keep{\i0}\N{\i1}me from the breeze, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ And blankets for my toeses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Take tweezers out{\i0}\N{\i1}of my valise ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and then massage{\i0}\N{\i1}my knobby knees. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ A bowl of peas!{\i0}\N{\i1}Some extra cheese! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ A cuddle with a Pekinese! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ A singing harp{\i0}\N{\i1}who's named Louise! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ A goat on skis!{\i0}\N{\i1}A new trapeze! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And more and more and{\i0}\N{\i1}more of these ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And just because I oughta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Make sure I'm{\i0}\N{\i1}drinking in the right ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Amount of fluids{\i0}\N{\i1}day and night ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ I wish I may, I wish I might
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Have just one little thing {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Oh will you please{\i0}\N{\i1}finally bring ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:14:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Me that tiny glass{\i0}\N{\i1}of water? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. This\Nis ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you even\Ncatch this flu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Inadequate hoof\Nand claw washing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be some\Nway to just cure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be a spell or\Na remedy in one of my books.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is one way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't think to\Nmention it earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Slipped my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On a hill at the very{\i0}\N{\i1}edge of Equestria,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there grows an{\i0}\N{\i1}exquisite magic flower.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pick the flower as it{\i0}\N{\i1}drops its petals at sunset.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then you can make a{\i0}\N{\i1}magical, soothing elixir{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to cure the Blue Flu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you have a good\Nreason you didn't bother
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to go get this flower
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as you\Nrealized you were sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I couldn't travel\Nthat far in my condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time I got\Nthere, I'd be too weak
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to even attempt to\Nretrieve the flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So where exactly are\NCadance and I headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you want to head north,\Nturn left at the--Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it would\Nbe much easier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,if I took you\Nthere myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were in\N"no condition" to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need to make\Nsome arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing OK there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm a\Nlittle out of practice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes to flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well! Then lucky for you,{\i0}\N{\i1}we're here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just at the\Ntop of that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry\Nabout this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was for us\Nto have some peaceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,quality time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I was looking\Nforward to it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's that flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hurry, we can still\Nhave some time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One last pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! Let's get Discord and\Nthis flower back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,then all our problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What in Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your coils off\Nmy sister-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of my sister-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't thank me yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And for good measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Better than\NOK, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get Discord\Nback to Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,make that elixir, and\Nfinally get a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to spend some quality\Ntime together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To the ends of Equestria!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To face such great danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And she did it for me.\NShe did it all for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For me! For me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,WERE...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,FAKING?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had a very\Ngood reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was in my\Nthinking tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I do most of\Nmy really deep thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was there and I\Nsaid to myself I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord, your friend Twilight\Nsays that she's your pal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but she never writes and she\Nnever pops in for a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know\Nwhere you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that she's a Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}maybe she's decided that{\i0}\N{\i1}she's too good for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never considered\Nmyself too good--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But how was I supposed to know
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for sure that I'm\Ntruly still friends
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with one of the most\Nimportant ponies around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not more--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,By seeing if you would go\Nto the ends of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,for me, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Which you did. Literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Twilight,\Nyou passed my friendship test!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the angry eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You love passing tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not because my little exam\Nput a damper on your visit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with Princess Cadance, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Made it so that there was\Nno time for you two
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to focus on your friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't put a damper\Non our visit at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't?\NHe didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Spending the day at the\NStarswirl the Bearded exhibit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,would have been more\Nrelaxing, but to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,relaxation is the\Nlast thing I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Life in the Crystal\NEmpire is wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's become a\Nlittle... predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoy a little\Nexcitement now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting to face all\Nthese challenges today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,was just what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And facing them with you just\Nmade me realize even more
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,how lucky I am to have\Nsomepony like you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not see each\Nother very often,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but I know you'll always\Nbe there when I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like she was\Nthere for you, Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She's a\Nreal sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all so lucky to\Nhave her in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think it's pretty clear that{\i0}\N{\i1}my visit with Cadance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't go quite the\Nway I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, I realized that\Nwhen you're with a good friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,even the most chaotic day can\Nend up being a great experience
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that brings you closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree, Discord?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:20:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go sayin'\Nyou got what you deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have no\Ntrouble saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You got what you\Ndeserved!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's learned his lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right,\Nmy little patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that you're back\Nfrom your trip, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just your presence here is\Nmaking me feel so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I trouble you for\Njust one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was simply going to ask for\Na teeny tiny glass of water.
